{
  "texts": [
    "This gives the investors a better chance to make wise decisions based on the companies' position and investment.",
    "Jones and Wang (2019) propose TreeNet method based on gradient boosting to perform classification tasks on private firms, which predicts the company's bankruptcy risk.",
    "As a result, their method can classify different measures of failure to analyze the company's risk before it files for bankruptcy.",
    "Arroyo et al. (2019) uses a timeaware analysis method to classify companies (as acquired, funding, or IPO) at their early stage to predict whether the company will be successful or not.",
    "The author uses a sliding window as a measure of time to give an estimate to the investors to decide on investment at the right stage of company's growth."
  ]
}